{"type": "file", "p": "Locomotive (Asia, Europe).rom", "n": "Locomotive (Asia, Europe)", "ext": ".rom", "parent": "", "urls": [{"u": "https://archive.org/download/CreatiVision_201809/ROMS.zip/Locomotive%20%28Asia%2C%20Europe%29.rom"}], "meta": {"path": "./Locomotive (Asia, Europe).rom", "name": "Locomotive", "desc": "Eres un prisionero en una fábrica de trenes y la única forma de escapar es construir tu propio tren. Debes correr por pasarelas peligrosas, a gran altura, y dejar caer todas las piezas correctas sobre las vías abajo, en el orden adecuado, si quieres sobrevivir. Los martillos, llaves y hasta los clavos que están por la fábrica están encantados y cobrarán vida para intentar martillar, apretar y clavarte. ¡Todo lo que tienes es una lata de aceite para destruirlos!", "genre": "Plataformas", "image": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Locomotive (Asia, Europe)-image.jpg", "video": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/videos/Locomotive (Asia, Europe)-video.mp4", "marquee": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Locomotive (Asia, Europe)-marquee.png", "thumbnail": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Locomotive (Asia, Europe)-thumb.jpg", "manual": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/manuals/Locomotive (Asia, Europe)-manual.pdf", "boxback": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Locomotive (Asia, Europe)-boxback.jpg", "rating": "0.65", "releasedate": "19830101T000000", "developer": "VTech", "publisher": "VTech", "players": "1-2", "md5": "e7e5d1e5dde349340144fa45a71e3ad2", "lang": "en", "region": "eu"}}
{"type": "file", "p": "Mouse Puzzle (Asia, Europe).rom", "n": "Mouse Puzzle (Asia, Europe)", "ext": ".rom", "parent": "", "urls": [{"u": "https://archive.org/download/CreatiVision_201809/ROMS.zip/Mouse%20Puzzle%20%28Asia%2C%20Europe%29.rom"}], "meta": {"path": "./Mouse Puzzle (Asia, Europe).rom", "name": "Mouse Puzzle", "desc": "Un pobre ratoncito tiene busca comida a través de las tuberías dentro de una pared, pero no consigue orientarse correctamente. Tu misión consiste en mover las tuberías para ayudarlo a ir en la dirección correcta. Sólo tú puedes ayudarlo a continuar. City Kitty es una gata malvada que se escabullirá por las tuberías y perseguirá a nuestro hambriento ratón. No dejes que la atrape porque él también tiene hambre y quiere ratón para cenar.", "genre": "Puzzle", "image": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Mouse Puzzle (Asia, Europe)-image.jpg", "video": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/videos/Mouse Puzzle (Asia, Europe)-video.mp4", "marquee": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Mouse Puzzle (Asia, Europe)-marquee.png", "thumbnail": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Mouse Puzzle (Asia, Europe)-thumb.jpg", "manual": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/manuals/Mouse Puzzle (Asia, Europe)-manual.pdf", "boxback": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Mouse Puzzle (Asia, Europe)-boxback.jpg", "rating": "0.75", "releasedate": "19820101T000000", "developer": "VTech", "publisher": "VTech", "players": "1-2", "md5": "da6816fd619ea095c56ad596720bd255", "lang": "en", "region": "eu"}}
{"type": "file", "p": "Music Maker (Asia, Europe).rom", "n": "Music Maker (Asia, Europe)", "ext": ".rom", "parent": "", "urls": [{"u": "https://archive.org/download/CreatiVision_201809/ROMS.zip/Music%20Maker%20%28Asia%2C%20Europe%29.rom"}], "meta": {"path": "./Music Maker (Asia, Europe).rom", "name": "Music Maker", "desc": "Selecciona instrumento, ritmo y tempo, y comienza a tocar. Simplemente presiona las teclas de notas indicadas en tu cuadrícula de Music Maker y reproduce la pieza de música que desees. Mientras tocas, las notas aparecerán en pantalla con la notación musical correcta y el instrumento elegido.", "genre": "Música y Baile / Ritmo", "image": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Music Maker (Asia, Europe)-image.jpg", "video": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/videos/Music Maker (Asia, Europe)-video.mp4", "marquee": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Music Maker (Asia, Europe)-marquee.png", "thumbnail": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Music Maker (Asia, Europe)-thumb.jpg", "manual": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/manuals/Music Maker (Asia, Europe)-manual.pdf", "boxback": "Z:/Digistorage/Arley4dCloudMedia/crvision/images/Music Maker (Asia, Europe)-boxback.jpg", "rating": "0.5", "releasedate": "19830101T000000", "developer": "VTech", "publisher": "VTech", "players": "1", "md5": "e7609cef5f705e8a529e6419ea710625", "lang": "en", "region": "eu"}}
